#828282;\n   194→            font-size: 11px;\n   195→        }\n   196→\n   197→        footer a {\n   198→            color: #000000;\n   199→            text-decoration: none;\n   200→            margin: 0 10px;\n   201→        }\n   202→\n   203→        footer a:hover {\n   204→            text-decoration: underline;\n   205→        }\n   206→\n   207→        .external-link {\n   208→            color: #828282;\n   209→            font-size: 10px;\n   210→            text-decoration: none;\n   211→        }\n   212→\n   213→        .external-link:hover {\n   214→            color: #ff6600;\n   215→        }\n   216→\n   217→        @media print {\n   218→            .three-column-layout {\n   219→                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n   220→            }\n   221→\n   222→            section {\n   223→                page-break-inside: avoid;\n   224→            }\n   225→        }\n   226→\n   227→        .highlight {\n   228→            background-color: #ffffd0;\n   229→            padding: 0 2px;\n   230→        }\n   231→\n   232→        .stat {\n   233→            color: #ff6600;\n   234→            font-weight: bold;\n   235→        }\n   236→    </style>\n   237→</head>\n   238→<body>\n   239→    <div class=\"container\">\n   240→        <header>\n   241→            <h1>Agentic Coding Research Report</h1>\n   242→            <div class=\"date\">February 23, 2026</div>\n   243→        </header>\n   244→\n   245→        <main class=\"three-column-layout\">\n   246→            <!-- Left Column: New Products -->\n   247→            <section class=\"new-products\">\n   248→                <h2>New Products (9)</h2>\n   249→\n   250→                <div class=\"item\">\n   251→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://openai.com\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI macOS Codex App</a></div>\n   252→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Dedicated macOS application for agentic coding with multi-agent collaboration, command center interface, and GPT-5.2-Codex model. Direct competitor to Claude Code.</div>\n   253→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   254→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">AI coding CLI</span>\n   255→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-02</span>\n   256→                    </div>\n   257→                    <div class=\"quote\">\"Multi-agent collaboration for complex development tasks\"</div>\n   258→                </div>\n   259→\n   260→                <div class=\"item\">\n   261→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/steveyegge/beads\" target=\"_blank\">Beads</a></div>\n   262→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Git-backed task/issue tracking system specifically designed for AI agents, solving agent memory loss problems with semantic 'memory decay' to summarize old tasks.</div>\n   263→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   264→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI tool</span>\n   265→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-04</span>\n   266→                    </div>\n   267→                    <div class=\"quote\"><span class=\"stat\">14,100+</span> GitHub stars. Built by Steve Yegge in just 6 days using Claude</div>\n   268→                </div>\n   269→\n   270→                <div class=\"item\">\n   271→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/xcode/\" target=\"_blank\">Xcode 26.3</a></div>\n   272→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Apple's IDE with native agentic coding integration, featuring Anthropic's Claude Agent and OpenAI's Codex models with MCP protocol support.</div>\n   273→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   274→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">IDE-integrated AI tools</span>\n   275→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-03</span>\n   276→                    </div>\n   277→                    <div class=\"quote\">\"Shift from AI assistant to autonomous collaborative partner\"</div>\n   278→                </div>\n   279→\n   280→                <div class=\"item\">\n   281→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">OpenClaw</a></div>\n   282→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Local AI agent platform with permanent memory using semantic search across memory files and dual-layer storage system.</div>\n   283→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   284→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI agent</span>\n   285→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-06</span>\n   286→                    </div>\n   287→                    <div class=\"quote\">Called <span class=\"highlight\">\"2026's most breakthrough AI Agent system\"</span></div>\n   288→                </div>\n   289→\n   290→                <div class=\"item\">\n   291→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://producthunt.com\" target=\"_blank\">Inspector</a></div>\n   292→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Visual editing tool that connects with AI assistants like Claude Code, Codex, and Cursor. Click UI elements to make visual adjustments that automatically write to codebase.</div>\n   293→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   294→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Visual AI coding tool</span>\n   295→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-08</span>\n   296→                    </div>\n   297→                    <div class=\"quote\"><span class=\"stat\">462</span> upvotes on Product Hunt. \"Figma for Claude Code\"</div>\n   298→                </div>\n   299→\n   300→                <div class=\"item\">\n   301→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/yan5xu/code-relay\" target=\"_blank\">Code Relay</a></div>\n   302→                    <div class=\"item-description\">AI Coding Agent protocol providing cross-session memory, multi-repo global awareness, and safe scoped execution. Compatible with OpenCode, Cursor, Claude Code, and Windsurf.</div>\n   303→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   304→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI agent</span>\n   305→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-10</span>\n   306→                    </div>\n   307→                    <div class=\"quote\">\"Provides cross-session memory for AI coding agents\"</div>\n   308→                </div>\n   309→\n   310→                <div class=\"item\">\n   311→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/research\" target=\"_blank\">Debug-gym</a></div>\n   312→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Microsoft Research environment for teaching AI coding tools how to debug code like programmers, addressing that developers spend most time debugging rather than writing code.</div>\n   313→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   314→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Workflow-specific AI tool</span>\n   315→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-10</span>\n   316→                    </div>\n   317→                    <div class=\"quote\">\"AI tools can propose fixes for hundreds of open issues\"</div>\n   318→                </div>\n   319→\n   320→                <div class=\"item\">\n   321→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">aivectormemory</a></div>\n   322→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Personal AI memory library that stores developer preferences and automatically retrieves memories for subsequent AI requests.</div>\n   323→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   324→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI tool</span>\n   325→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-15</span>\n   326→                    </div>\n   327→                    <div class=\"quote\">Addresses the \"last 100 meters\" problem of general model personalization</div>\n   328→                </div>\n   329→\n   330→                <div class=\"item\">\n   331→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3.5\" target=\"_blank\">Qwen Code</a></div>\n   332→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Open-source AI agent specifically optimized for terminals, part of the Qwen-Agent ecosystem for building LLM applications.</div>\n   333→                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   334→                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI agent</span>\n   335→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-17</span>\n   336→                    </div>\n   337→                </div>\n   338→            </section>\n   339→\n   340→            <!-- Middle Column: Whitelist Updates -->\n   341→            <section class=\"whitelist-updates\">\n   342→                <h2>Whitelist Updates</h2>\n   343→                <div class=\"no-content\">No whitelist updates available for this period.</div>\n   344→            </section>\n   345→\n   346→            <!-- Right Column: Technical Insights -->\n   347→            <section class=\"technical-insights\">\n   348→                <h2>Technical Insights (11)</h2>\n   349→\n   350→                <div class=\"item\">\n   351→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7602259669730541595\" target=\"_blank\">2026年2月AI编码工具三国杀</a></div>\n   352→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Claude Code Opus 4.6发布Agent Teams和1M token上下文窗口，Cursor 2.3+Composer 1.5引入Shadow Workspace和Plan Mode，Copilot占68%市场份额。</div>\n   353→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   354→                        <span class=\"author\">Tech Media</span>\n   355→                        <a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7602259669730541595\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Analysis</a>\n   356→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-19</span>\n   357→                    </div>\n   358→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   359→                        <span class=\"topic\">Claude Code</span>\n   360→                        <span class=\"topic\">Cursor</span>\n   361→                        <span class=\"topic\">multi-agent</span>\n   362→                    </div>\n   363→                </div>\n   364→\n   365→                <div class=\"item\">\n   366→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7603373016365482530/\" target=\"_blank\">Vibe Coding终结，Agentic Engineering时代开启</a></div>\n   367→                    <div class=\"item-description\">Karpathy宣布Vibe Coding时代结束，99%代码由AI接管，进入Agentic Engineering新范式。</div>\n   368→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   369→                        <span class=\"author\">Andrej Karpathy</span>\n   370→                        <a href=\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7603373016365482530/\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>\n   371→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-18</span>\n   372→                    </div>\n   373→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   374→                        <span class=\"topic\">Agentic Engineering</span>\n   375→                        <span class=\"topic\">paradigm shift</span>\n   376→                    </div>\n   377→                </div>\n   378→\n   379→                <div class=\"item\">\n   380→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://x.com/karpathy/status/2024583544157458452\" target=\"_blank\">LLM改变软件开发约束</a></div>\n   381→                    <div class=\"item-description\">编程语言研究的最佳时代，LLM正在改变软件开发的约束条件。提及nanochat项目：GitHub星标43,475。</div>\n   382→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   383→                        <span class=\"author\">Andrej Karpathy</span>\n   384→                        <a href=\"https://x.com/karpathy/status/2024583544157458452\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>\n   385→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-18</span>\n   386→                    </div>\n   387→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   388→                        <span class=\"topic\">LLM constraints</span>\n   389→                        <span class=\"topic\">nanochat</span>\n   390→                    </div>\n   391→                </div>\n   392→\n   393→                <div class=\"item\">\n   394→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://m.163.com/dy/article/KKU06RJI0551ABV6.html\" target=\"_blank\">Claude Code之父对谈Karpathy</a></div>\n   395→                    <div class=\"item-description\">20年编程工作流在几周内被颠覆：80%代码由AI编写。警告\"Slopacolypse\"（垃圾代码末日）风险。</div>\n   396→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   397→                        <span class=\"author\">Karpathy, Cherny</span>\n   398→                        <a href=\"https://m.163.com/dy/article/KKU06RJI0551ABV6.html\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Podcast</a>\n   399→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-17</span>\n   400→                    </div>\n   401→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   402→                        <span class=\"topic\">Claude Code</span>\n   403→                        <span class=\"topic\">code quality</span>\n   404→                    </div>\n   405→                </div>\n   406→\n   407→                <div class=\"item\">\n   408→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7608178484015382568\" target=\"_blank\">2026年AI Agent开发工具生态全景</a></div>\n   409→                    <div class=\"item-description\">市场从\"AI助手\"向真正自主\"AI Agent\"演进。工具专业化趋势明显，API聚合平台兴起，中国企业级方案崛起。</div>\n   410→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   411→                        <span class=\"author\">Dev Community</span>\n   412→                        <a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7608178484015382568\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Tech Blog</a>\n   413→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-17</span>\n   414→                    </div>\n   415→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   416→                        <span class=\"topic\">ecosystem</span>\n   417→                        <span class=\"topic\">enterprise</span>\n   418→                    </div>\n   419→                </div>\n   420→\n   421→                <div class=\"item\">\n   422→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002eum5fCXBMVm-_4O8x24UR-_N8BAIBvsiF3sqhMnZtMid0__\" target=\"_blank\">Amjad Masad：从\"怎么做\"到\"做什么\"</a></div>\n   423→                    <div class=\"item-description\">从\"告诉AI如何做事\"转向\"告诉AI做什么\"。预计人类编程角色约2年内可能出现负增长。</div>\n   424→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   425→                        <span class=\"author\">Amjad Masad</span>\n   426→                        <a href=\"https://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002eum5fCXBMVm-_4O8x24UR-_N8BAIBvsiF3sqhMnZtMid0__\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Interview</a>\n   427→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-15</span>\n   428→                    </div>\n   429→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   430→                        <span class=\"topic\">Replit</span>\n   431→                        <span class=\"topic\">paradigm</span>\n   432→                    </div>\n   433→                </div>\n   434→\n   435→                <div class=\"item\">\n   436→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000046630992\" target=\"_blank\">Django之父6大预测</a></div>\n   437→                    <div class=\"item-description\">1年内AI Agent将实际落地，3年内有人将借助GenAI工具获得普利策奖，6年内可能引发社会危机。</div>\n   438→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   439→                        <span class=\"author\">Simon Willison</span>\n   440→                        <a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000046630992\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Blog</a>\n   441→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-14</span>\n   442→                    </div>\n   443→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   444→                        <span class=\"topic\">AI agents</span>\n   445→                        <span class=\"topic\">AGI risks</span>\n   446→                    </div>\n   447→                </div>\n   448→\n   449→                <div class=\"item\">\n   450→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/1712150\" target=\"_blank\">编程已死？2026年AI技术趋势预测</a></div>\n   451→                    <div class=\"item-description\">1年内LLM生成代码质量将\"无可辩驳地优秀\"，6年内手写代码可能成为历史。</div>\n   452→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   453→                        <span class=\"author\">Simon Willison</span>\n   454→                        <a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/1712150\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Blog</a>\n   455→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-13</span>\n   456→                    </div>\n   457→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   458→                        <span class=\"topic\">predictions</span>\n   459→                        <span class=\"topic\">LLM quality</span>\n   460→                    </div>\n   461→                </div>\n   462→\n   463→                <div class=\"item\">\n   464→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.09345v1\" target=\"_blank\">AgentCgroup研究</a></div>\n   465→                    <div class=\"item-description\">首次系统研究AI agent资源动态。工具调用占56-74%延迟，内存是主要瓶颈，峰值-平均内存波动达15.4倍。</div>\n   466→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   467→                        <span class=\"author\">Research</span>\n   468→                        <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.09345v1\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">ArXiv</a>\n   469→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-10</span>\n   470→                    </div>\n   471→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   472→                        <span class=\"topic\">resource mgmt</span>\n   473→                        <span class=\"topic\">memory</span>\n   474→                    </div>\n   475→                </div>\n   476→\n   477→                <div class=\"item\">\n   478→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://www.donews.com/news/detail/8/6394371.html\" target=\"_blank\">GPT-5.3-Codex vs Claude Opus 4.6</a></div>\n   479→                    <div class=\"item-description\">OpenAI和Anthropic同日对决。开发者报告复杂任务10倍速度提升，AI编码工具从实验助手变为必需开发伙伴。</div>\n   480→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   481→                        <span class=\"author\">Industry News</span>\n   482→                        <a href=\"https://www.donews.com/news/detail/8/6394371.html\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Tech Media</a>\n   483→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-06</span>\n   484→                    </div>\n   485→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   486→                        <span class=\"topic\">OpenAI</span>\n   487→                        <span class=\"topic\">Anthropic</span>\n   488→                    </div>\n   489→                </div>\n   490→\n   491→                <div class=\"item\">\n   492→                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1bqFPzCEHz/\" target=\"_blank\">Lex Fridman Podcast #490</a></div>\n   493→                    <div class=\"item-description\">4小时超长访谈，涵盖中美AI竞争、ChatGPT vs Claude vs Gemini vs Gemini对比、AGI时间线预测2030年达到人类水平。</div>\n   494→                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n   495→                        <span class=\"author\">Fridman, Raschka, Lambert</span>\n   496→                        <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1bqFPzCEHz/\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Podcast</a>\n   497→                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-01</span>\n   498→                    </div>\n   499→                    <div class=\"topics\">\n   500→                        <span class=\"topic\">AI现状</span>\n   501→                        <span class=\"topic\">AGI</span>\n   502→                    </div>\n   503→                </div>\n   504→            </section>\n   505→        </main>\n   506→\n   507→        <footer>\n   508→            <a href=\"#\">Archives</a>\n   509→            <a href=\"#\">About</a>\n   510→            <a href=\"#\">RSS Feed</a>\n   511→            <a href=\"#\">Contact</a>\n   512→            <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n   513→                Generated with Claude Code | <a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>\n   514→            </div>\n   515→        </footer>\n   516→    </div>\n   517→</body>\n   518→</html>\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"
      }
    ]
