      "filePath": "/home/runner/work/agentdaily/agentdaily/updates/2026-02-23/index.html",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Agentic Coding Research Report - 2026-02-23</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f6f6ef;\n            color: #000000;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n            font-size: 13px;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1400px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 10px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: #ff6600;\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #000000;\n        }\n\n        header .date {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            color: #000000;\n            margin-top: 3px;\n        }\n\n        .three-column-layout {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 40% 35% 25%;\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 1024px) {\n            .three-column-layout {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n\n        section {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border: 1px solid #d4d4d4;\n            padding: 10px;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #000000;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #ff6600;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .item {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            border-bottom: 1px dotted #d4d4d4;\n        }\n\n        .item:last-child {\n            border-bottom: none;\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n\n        .item-title {\n            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n            font-size: 13px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .item-title a {\n            color: #000000;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .item-title a:visited {\n            color: #828282;\n        }\n\n        .item-title a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        .item-description {\n            color: #000000;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n        }\n\n        .item-meta {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            color: #828282;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .category-tag {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #f6f6ef;\n            color: #828282;\n            padding: 2px 6px;\n            font-size: 10px;\n            margin-right: 5px;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            border: 1px solid #d4d4d4;\n        }\n\n        .quote {\n            color: #828282;\n            font-style: italic;\n            font-size: 11px;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            padding-left: 10px;\n            border-left: 2px solid #ff6600;\n        }\n\n        .insight-meta {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .author {\n            color: #828282;\n            font-size: 11px;\n        }\n\n        .source {\n            color: #ff6600;\n            font-size: 10px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .source:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        .published-date {\n            color: #828282;\n            font-size: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .topics {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .topic {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n            color: #666;\n            padding: 2px 5px;\n            font-size: 9px;\n            margin-right: 3px;\n            margin-bottom: 3px;\n        }\n\n        .no-content {\n            color: #828282;\n            font-style: italic;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #f6f6ef;\n            border-top: 1px solid #d4d4d4;\n            padding: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #828282;\n            font-size: 11px;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: #000000;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        .external-link {\n            color: #828282;\n            font-size: 10px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .external-link:hover {\n            color: #ff6600;\n        }\n\n        @media print {\n            .three-column-layout {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n\n            section {\n                page-break-inside: avoid;\n            }\n        }\n\n        .highlight {\n            background-color: #ffffd0;\n            padding: 0 2px;\n        }\n\n        .stat {\n            color: #ff6600;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <header>\n            <h1>Agentic Coding Research Report</h1>\n            <div class=\"date\">February 23, 2026</div>\n        </header>\n\n        <main class=\"three-column-layout\">\n            <!-- Left Column: New Products -->\n            <section class=\"new-products\">\n                <h2>New Products (9)</h2>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://openai.com\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI macOS Codex App</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Dedicated macOS application for agentic coding with multi-agent collaboration, command center interface, and GPT-5.2-Codex model. Direct competitor to Claude Code.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">AI coding CLI</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-02</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\">\"Multi-agent collaboration for complex development tasks\"</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/steveyegge/beads\" target=\"_blank\">Beads</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Git-backed task/issue tracking system specifically designed for AI agents, solving agent memory loss problems with semantic 'memory decay' to summarize old tasks.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI tool</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-04</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\"><span class=\"stat\">14,100+</span> GitHub stars. Built by Steve Yegge in just 6 days using Claude</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/xcode/\" target=\"_blank\">Xcode 26.3</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Apple's IDE with native agentic coding integration, featuring Anthropic's Claude Agent and OpenAI's Codex models with MCP protocol support.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">IDE-integrated AI tools</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-03</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\">\"Shift from AI assistant to autonomous collaborative partner\"</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">OpenClaw</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Local AI agent platform with permanent memory using semantic search across memory files and dual-layer storage system.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI agent</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-06</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\">Called <span class=\"highlight\">\"2026's most breakthrough AI Agent system\"</span></div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://producthunt.com\" target=\"_blank\">Inspector</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Visual editing tool that connects with AI assistants like Claude Code, Codex, and Cursor. Click UI elements to make visual adjustments that automatically write to codebase.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Visual AI coding tool</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-08</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\"><span class=\"stat\">462</span> upvotes on Product Hunt. \"Figma for Claude Code\"</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/yan5xu/code-relay\" target=\"_blank\">Code Relay</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">AI Coding Agent protocol providing cross-session memory, multi-repo global awareness, and safe scoped execution. Compatible with OpenCode, Cursor, Claude Code, and Windsurf.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI agent</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-10</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\">\"Provides cross-session memory for AI coding agents\"</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/research\" target=\"_blank\">Debug-gym</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Microsoft Research environment for teaching AI coding tools how to debug code like programmers, addressing that developers spend most time debugging rather than writing code.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Workflow-specific AI tool</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-10</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\">\"AI tools can propose fixes for hundreds of open issues\"</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">aivectormemory</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Personal AI memory library that stores developer preferences and automatically retrieves memories for subsequent AI requests.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI tool</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-15</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"quote\">Addresses the \"last 100 meters\" problem of general model personalization</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen3.5\" target=\"_blank\">Qwen Code</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Open-source AI agent specifically optimized for terminals, part of the Qwen-Agent ecosystem for building LLM applications.</div>\n                    <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"category-tag\">Open-source AI agent</span>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-17</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <!-- Middle Column: Whitelist Updates -->\n            <section class=\"whitelist-updates\">\n                <h2>Whitelist Updates</h2>\n                <div class=\"no-content\">No whitelist updates available for this period.</div>\n            </section>\n\n            <!-- Right Column: Technical Insights -->\n            <section class=\"technical-insights\">\n                <h2>Technical Insights (11)</h2>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7602259669730541595\" target=\"_blank\">2026年2月AI编码工具三国杀</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Claude Code Opus 4.6发布Agent Teams和1M token上下文窗口，Cursor 2.3+Composer 1.5引入Shadow Workspace和Plan Mode，Copilot占68%市场份额。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Tech Media</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7602259669730541595\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Technical Analysis</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-19</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">Claude Code</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">Cursor</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">multi-agent</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7603373016365482530/\" target=\"_blank\">Vibe Coding终结，Agentic Engineering时代开启</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">Karpathy宣布Vibe Coding时代结束，99%代码由AI接管，进入Agentic Engineering新范式。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Andrej Karpathy</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://m.toutiao.com/article/7603373016365482530/\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-18</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">Agentic Engineering</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">paradigm shift</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://x.com/karpathy/status/2024583544157458452\" target=\"_blank\">LLM改变软件开发约束</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">编程语言研究的最佳时代，LLM正在改变软件开发的约束条件。提及nanochat项目：GitHub星标43,475。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Andrej Karpathy</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://x.com/karpathy/status/2024583544157458452\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-18</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">LLM constraints</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">nanochat</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://m.163.com/dy/article/KKU06RJI0551ABV6.html\" target=\"_blank\">Claude Code之父对谈Karpathy</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">20年编程工作流在几周内被颠覆：80%代码由AI编写。警告\"Slopacolypse\"（垃圾代码末日）风险。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Karpathy, Cherny</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://m.163.com/dy/article/KKU06RJI0551ABV6.html\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Podcast</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-17</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">Claude Code</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">code quality</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7608178484015382568\" target=\"_blank\">2026年AI Agent开发工具生态全景</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">市场从\"AI助手\"向真正自主\"AI Agent\"演进。工具专业化趋势明显，API聚合平台兴起，中国企业级方案崛起。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Dev Community</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/7608178484015382568\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Tech Blog</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-17</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">ecosystem</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">enterprise</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002eum5fCXBMVm-_4O8x24UR-_N8BAIBvsiF3sqhMnZtMid0__\" target=\"_blank\">Amjad Masad：从\"怎么做\"到\"做什么\"</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">从\"告诉AI如何做事\"转向\"告诉AI做什么\"。预计人类编程角色约2年内可能出现负增长。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Amjad Masad</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002eum5fCXBMVm-_4O8x24UR-_N8BAIBvsiF3sqhMnZtMid0__\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Interview</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-15</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">Replit</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">paradigm</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000046630992\" target=\"_blank\">Django之父6大预测</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">1年内AI Agent将实际落地，3年内有人将借助GenAI工具获得普利策奖，6年内可能引发社会危机。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Simon Willison</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000046630992\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Blog</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-14</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">AI agents</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">AGI risks</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/1712150\" target=\"_blank\">编程已死？2026年AI技术趋势预测</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">1年内LLM生成代码质量将\"无可辩驳地优秀\"，6年内手写代码可能成为历史。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Simon Willison</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/1712150\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Blog</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-13</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">predictions</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">LLM quality</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.09345v1\" target=\"_blank\">AgentCgroup研究</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">首次系统研究AI agent资源动态。工具调用占56-74%延迟，内存是主要瓶颈，峰值-平均内存波动达15.4倍。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Research</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/html/2602.09345v1\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">ArXiv</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-10</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">resource mgmt</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">memory</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://www.donews.com/news/detail/8/6394371.html\" target=\"_blank\">GPT-5.3-Codex vs Claude Opus 4.6</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">OpenAI和Anthropic同日对决。开发者报告复杂任务10倍速度提升，AI编码工具从实验助手变为必需开发伙伴。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Industry News</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://www.donews.com/news/detail/8/6394371.html\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Tech Media</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-06</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">OpenAI</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">Anthropic</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"item\">\n                    <div class=\"item-title\"><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1bqFPzCEHz/\" target=\"_blank\">Lex Fridman Podcast #490</a></div>\n                    <div class=\"item-description\">4小时超长访谈，涵盖中美AI竞争、ChatGPT vs Claude vs Gemini vs Gemini对比、AGI时间线预测2030年达到人类水平。</div>\n                    <div class=\"insight-meta\">\n                        <span class=\"author\">Fridman, Raschka, Lambert</span>\n                        <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1bqFPzCEHz/\" class=\"source\" target=\"_blank\">Podcast</a>\n                        <span class=\"published-date\">2026-02-01</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"topics\">\n                        <span class=\"topic\">AI现状</span>\n                        <span class=\"topic\">AGI</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n        </main>\n\n        <footer>\n            <a href=\"#\">Archives</a>\n            <a href=\"#\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#\">RSS Feed</a>\n            <a href=\"#\">Contact</a>\n            <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n                Generated with Claude Code | <a href=\"https://github.com\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
